## FEC API Overview

**Official Source**: Federal Election Commission - authoritative U.S. campaign finance data
**Coverage**: Federal elections (President, Senate, House) from 1980s to present
**Data Types**: Contributions, expenditures, candidate financials, PAC/Super PAC spending

**Best For**:
- Campaign contribution tracking ("Who donated to Senator X?")
- PAC and Super PAC spending analysis
- Candidate fundraising totals
- Independent expenditures (outside spending)
- Follow-the-money investigations

