## Query Parameters

**candidate_name** (string, required even if empty "")
- Last name or full name of candidate
- Examples: "Warren", "Elizabeth Warren", "Biden"
- Leave empty ("") if not searching for specific candidate

**committee_name** (string, required even if empty "")
- Name of PAC, Super PAC, or campaign committee
- Examples: "Priorities USA", "Senate Majority PAC"
- Leave empty ("") if not searching for specific committee

**contributor_name** (string, required even if empty "")
- Name of donor/contributor to search
- Examples: "Elon Musk", "Goldman Sachs", "Gates Foundation"
- Leave empty ("") if not searching for specific donor

**office** (string or null)
- Office sought by candidate
- Values: "P" (President), "S" (Senate), "H" (House), or null
- Use null if not filtering by office

**state** (string or null)
- Two-letter state code (e.g., "MA", "CA", "TX")
- Use null if not filtering by state

**cycle** (integer, required)
- Election cycle year (2024, 2022, 2020, 2018, 2016, etc.)
- Even-numbered years only
- Use most recent cycle (2024) unless question specifies

**party** (string or null)
- Party affiliation
- Values: "DEM" (Democrat), "REP" (Republican), "IND" (Independent), "LIB" (Libertarian), "GRE" (Green), or null
- Use null if not filtering by party

